      "title": "World Bank pledges assistance to Sri Lanka",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The World Bank will provide further assistance after reaching an agreement with the International Monetary Fund, said Faris Godot-Servos, World Bank's Director for Sri Lanka.",
        "The above was stated during the discussion held yesterday (29) between the representatives of the World Bank and President Gotabaya Rajapaksa at the Presidential Palace in Colombo."
      ],
